Confu has launched high-end hair dryer series such as K9 and K10, which use a high-speed digital brushless motor with a speed of 110,000 rpm, marking the official entry into the high-end national hair dryer brand.
Confu hair dryer is highly praised and recommended by the stars of Hunan Satellite TV#’s dear’s inn’s variety show;
Won the honorary title of 'Guangdong Provincial Intellectual Property Demonstration Enterprise'; in the same year, it successfully identified the 'Guangdong Provincial Engineering Technology R&D Center' and was awarded the honorary title of 'National Intellectual Property Advantage Enterprise';
Won the honorary title of 'Liangzhu Enterprise in the Airport Economic Zone' and the honorary title of 'Guangdong Contract-abiding and Credit-keeping Enterprise'
Won the honorary title of 'Guangdong Province Intellectual Property Advantage Enterprise'; in the same year, the company passed the 'Intellectual Property Management System' certification;
The company has passed the certification of the 'Integration of Industrialization and Industrialization Management System' by the Ministry of Industry and Information Technology of the People's Republic of China, and won the title of 'Innovative Enterprise in Guangdong Province' in the same year; won the honorary titles of 'Glorious Taxpayer' and 'Liangzhu Enterprise in Airport Economic Zone';
In-depth cooperation between Yasuo and Hunan Satellite TV, Yasuo's hair dryer is the official designated product of the reality show of 'The Whirlwind Dutiful Son';
Won the honorary titles of 'Quality Improvement, Brand Creation, Standardization Enterprise', 'Enthusiastic Consumer Public Welfare Advanced Collective' and other honorary titles;
The company was awarded the title of 'The Third Batch of Key High-growth SMEs in Guangdong Province';
'Confu' won the title of 'National High-tech Enterprise';
'Confu' won the title of 'China Quality and Integrity Enterprise' and the title of 'Military Material Mobilization Procurement Supplier', and established the official flagship store of Confu on Taobao, Tmall, Jingdong and other major platforms;
The company became a member of the National Household Appliances Standardization Committee, participated in the formulation and drafting of 'standards', and was awarded the title of 'Guangdong Province Superior Traditional Transformation and Upgrading Demonstration Enterprise';
Won the title of 'Famous Brand Product of Guangdong Province', 'Famous Brand of China' and 'Famous Brand of China';
Won the title of 'Guangdong Province Contract-abiding and Trustworthy Enterprise';
Was rated as 'European Information Center Registered Supplier' by China Council for the Promotion of International Trade and European Information Center;
'Confu' has completed trademark registration in 31 countries around the world;
We hired 'World Hairdressing Master' Mr. Lai Wei'an as the brand spokesperson to put in advertising on CCTV, Hunan Satellite TV and other domestic first-line satellite TVs; in the same year, he was awarded the honorary title of 'Guangdong Private Technology Enterprise';
'Confu' passed the 'CE' certification of 'RWTUV' in Germany; 'GS' certification of 'TUV' in Germany; 'CE' certification of 'ETL' of the United States and the EU ROHS certification; Confu began to enter overseas markets;
Successfully passed ISO9001 quality management system and Great Wall certification;
Officially registered the 'Confu' brand;
Established, gradually from a small workshop to having its own 'Tai Mao' small workshop and assembly line;
Chairman Huang Huaqun started his journey to Confu in a simple bungalow in Tangpu Village, Yuhu Town, Jieyang, Guangdong;
